descriptionNullable:
# Introduction

The funny green frog of fun has entered Kaggle datasets. Go ahead and use it however you see fit! Here you are provided with with +2300 JPEG images of pepe the frog. Images are scaled to have max dimensions of 512x512. 

# Tasks 

- Generate unique and insanely rare pepe images using ML.
- Use CLIP-like model in order to predict the `000000_file_names.jpg` for each image.
- Cluster images into groups, find out what these groups have in common.
- Download all of the images to your hard-drive for safekeeping.

But, most importantly... **have FUN**!
title: REEE dataset (pepe edition)
subtitle: Pepe memes, 512x512 format in JPEG
